HEADWORD: Scone
<hw>Scone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A cake, thinner than a
bannock, made of wheat or barley or oat meal.</def> <altsp>[Written
variously, <asp>scon</asp>, <asp>skone</asp>, <asp>skon</asp>,
etc.]</altsp> <mark>[Scot.]</mark> <rj><au>Burns.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

